{"id":"316153841_3D_Model_Indexing_in_Videos_for_Content-Based_Retrieval_via_X3D-Based_Semantic_Enrichment_and_Automated_Reasoning","abstract":"3D models play an important role in a wide range of applications from engineering to training, from visualization to entertainment. The formal representation of, and reasoning over, concepts and properties associated with 3D models can contribute to next-generation 3D scene understanding, classification, indexing, and retrieval via 3D characteristics as opposed to keywords of traditional retrieval methods. This paper introduces a novel 3D model indexing method with X3D-alignment, with an emphasis on the representation, annotation, and efficient content-based retrieval of 3D models and their regions of interest from computer animations.","authors":["Leslie F. Sikos"],"meta":["June 2017","DOI:10.1145/3055624.3075943","Conference: 22nd International Conference on 3D Web TechnologyAt: Brisbane, Australia"],"references":["292603742_3D_Reconstruction_from_3D_Cultural_Heritage_Models","284243611_Cluster_rendering_on_large_high-resolution_multi-displays_using_X3DOM_and_HTML","284168138_A_Novel_Approach_to_Multimedia_Ontology_Engineering_for_Automated_Reasoning_over_Audiovisual_LOD_Datasets","281489532_Conceptual_knowledge-based_modeling_of_interactive_3D_content","280627306_Knowledge-Driven_Video_Information_Retrieval_with_LOD_From_Semi-Structured_to_Structured_Video_Metadata","265802710_Advanced_XHTML5_Metadata_and_Semantics_for_Web_30_Videos","235697561_Acquisition_of_multimedia_ontology_An_application_in_preservation_of_cultural_heritage","232625844_Coupling_Ontologies_with_Graphics_Content_for_Knowledge_Driven_Visualization","232614678_A_common_ontology_for_multi-dimensional_shapes","225601366_A_survey_of_content_based_3D_shape_retrieval_methods","221393491_The_even_more_irresistible_SROIQ","220921168_Integration_of_OWL_ontologies_in_MPEG-7_and_TV-Anytime_compliant_Semantic_Indexing","200688596_Semantic_Integration_and_Retrieval